Package org.eclipse.jface.viewers

Class ColumnLayoutData

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.jface.viewers.ColumnLayoutData
Direct Known Subclasses:
ColumnPixelData, ColumnWeightData
@NoExtend public abstract class ColumnLayoutData extends Object
An abstract column layout data describing the information needed (by TableLayout) to properly lay out a table.

This class is not intended to be subclassed outside the framework.
